  "instructions": [
    "Heat olive oil in a kazan cauldron over medium heat.",
    "Add diced onion and cook until translucent.",
    "Stir in minced garlic and diced carrots, cooking for 2 minutes.",
    "Toss in chopped Savoy cabbage and stir until it begins to wilt.",
    "Pour in vegetable stock and bring the mixture to a boil.",
    "Reduce the heat and stir in coconut milk, turmeric, smoked paprika, sea salt, and black pepper.",
    "Simmer gently for 20 minutes until the cabbage is tender.",
    "In a small bowl, dissolve agar-agar powder in 2 tbsp water and stir it into the soup.",
    "Continue simmering for an additional 5 minutes until the soup thickens.",
    "Let the soup cool to room temperature, then refrigerate for 2 hours until it sets into a frosted jelly-like consistency."
  ],
